(5227, 11, 'Odour emissions could be reduced by using additives', 'Low price, easy to use and the diversity of additives proposed make them very attractive for pig breeders. Since several\r\nyears, ITP achieved studies concerning additiveâ€™s efficiency concerning odour emissions in pig units. The following one\r\nwas realized in commercial plant on growing-finishing rooms. Comparison between reference and treated room shows\r\na reduction of 30 % odour emission for the treated room with variability between measurements.', 'Guingand N;Veyrier T;', 'Vol.27 4', 0, '2004  juillet-aoÃ»t', '651', 'additifs;conditions d''Ã©levage;engraissement;environnement;odeurs;Ã©missions;', '', '', '', 'n', '', 'o'),
