(5201, 15, 'Identificaiton of Belgian pigs : Sanitel covers all farms', 'In an unfavourable socio-economic context and despite a weakly structured professional organisation, Belgium has succeeded in setting up an effective system of pork traceability. Today, Sanitel Porc covers the whole country and all the farms, and provides good traceability of animal movements and health monitoring of herds.', 'Dagorn J;', 'Vol.23 5', 0, '2004', '625', 'Belgique;identification;SANITEL;traÃ§abilitÃ©;Ã©levages;', '', '', '', 'n', '', 'o');
